| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-0320 — Recovery Inhibition (direwolf)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: dce6ee3d-1ad4-5d83-8bbf-0baca3e40fac"
